*     /merchant/merProductType/edit/{id}/{pageNumber}     merchant.MerProductTypeController.edit
*     /merchant/merProductType/update/{id}                merchant.MerProductTypeController.update

#   Merchant Brand 管理
*     /system/brands                                      system.BrandController.index
